{"title":"徐水参观有感","authors":["沈钧儒　陈叔通"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐水参观有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈钧儒　陈叔通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争说人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我闻徐水已开端；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此行亲眼来观看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞跃心情胜激湍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理想都能成现实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂惟岁岁大丰穰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农商学兵一体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此真能到富强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想解放是先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲才能向上冲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有党先来领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民从此信心浓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壁画诗歌尽动人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最为难得感情真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬蓬勃勃皆生气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱社如家自有因。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}